title: SPY DROPS PSYCHEDELIC FADE TO BLACK COLLECTION
description:
Amidst the feedback, distortion, and raised volume of life, lies consciousness. Shade your eyes from the first rays of the new rising sun with resplendent colors, letting your mind wander across the (rainbow) bridge connecting rock 'n' roll and the metaphysical. Vibrant Spectra lenses wrapped in translucent cosmic overtones burn bright, and Fade to Black. 

Check out the whole sampling at www.spyoptic.com/collection/fadetoblack.­html
